<i>Something you love better than me.</i>

3389
03:47:58,048 --> 03:47:59,276
<i>The red earth of Tara.</i>

3390
03:47:59,349 --> 03:48:00,976
<i>- Tara!
- Tara!</i>

3391
03:48:04,588 --> 03:48:05,748
Tara!

3392
03:48:06,890 --> 03:48:08,050
Home!

3393
03:48:09,259 --> 03:48:10,783
I'll go home!

3394
03:48:11,795 --> 03:48:14,423
And I'll think of some way to get him back.

3395
03:48:15,065 --> 03:48:16,430
After all...

3396
03:48:17,000 --> 03:48:19,594
tomorrow is another day.

